'''CF Granma''' is a [[Cuba]]n [[association football|football]] team playing in the [[Campeonato Nacional de Fútbol de Cuba|Cuban National Football League]] and representing [[Granma Province]]. They play their home games at the [[Mártires de Barbados Stadium|Estadio Mártires de Barbados]] in [[Bayamo]] or at the Conrado Benítez in [[Jiguaní]].

==History==
Nicknamed ''Los Incansables'',<ref>[http://www.cnctv.icrt.cu/.../incansables-quieren-colarse-los-seis-la-elite%2F&usg=AOvVaw0OCAT2vxsOK_pqcoqElX48 Incansables quieren colarse entre los seis de la élite] - CNC TV Granma {{es|icon}}</ref> the team never won the national league title, but was runner-up in 2002.<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/cubachamp.html Cuba - List of Champions] - RSSSF</ref>

