{{Infobox football biography | name = Rangelo Janga | image = | caption = | fullname = Rangelo Maria Janga<ref>{{cite news | title = Elroy Room en Joel Saro geselecteerd door bondscoach Patrick Kluivert voor Curaçao | url = http://www.hetgeldersevoetbal.nl/elroy-room-en-joel-saro-geselecteerd-door-bondscoach-patrick-kluivert-voor-curacao/ | publisher = Het voetbalportaal van Gelderland | language = [[Dutch language|Dutch]] | date = 16 May 2016 | accessdate = 25 May 2016}}</ref> | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1992|4|16|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Rotterdam]], [[Netherlands]] | height = {{height|m=1.95}} | position = [[Striker (association football)|Striker]] | currentclub = [[FC Astana|Astana]] | clubnumber = 32 | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[SBV Excelsior]] | youthyears2 = | youthclubs2 = [[Willem II Tilburg|Willem II]] | years1 = 2010–2012 | clubs1 = [[Willem II Tilburg|Willem II]] | caps1 = 24 | goals1 = 3 | years2 = 2012 | clubs2 = → [[SBV Excelsior|Excelsior]] (loan) | caps2 = 16 | goals2 = 2 | years3 = 2012–2014 | clubs3 = [[SBV Excelsior|Excelsior]] | caps3 = 36 | goals3 = 3 | years4 = 2014–2015 | clubs4 = [[Omonia Aradippou]] | caps4 = 26 | goals4 = 5 | years5 = 2015–2016 | clubs5 = [[FC Dordrecht]] | caps5 = 34 | goals5 = 21 | years6 = 2016–2017 | clubs6 = [[FK AS Trenčín|Trenčín]] | caps6 = 48 | goals6 = 28 | years7 = 2018 | clubs7 = [[K.A.A. Gent|Gent]] | caps7 = 17 | goals7 = 5 | years8 = 2018– | clubs8 = [[FC Astana|Astana]] | caps8 = 10 | goals8 = 4 | nationalyears1 = 2016– | nationalteam1 = [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao]] | nationalcaps1 = 14 | nationalgoals1 = 10 | club-update = 20 May 2018 | ntupdate = 19 November 2018 }} '''Rangelo Maria Janga''' (born 16 April 1992) is a [[Curaçao]]an professional [[association football|footballer]], who currently plays for [[FC Astana|Astana]].<ref>https://sport.sme.sk/c/20725498/fortuna-liga-2017-2018-rangelo-janga-mieri-do-kaa-gent.html</ref> He formerly played for [[Willem II Tilburg|Willem II]], [[SBV Excelsior|Excelsior]], [[Omonia Aradippou]] and [[FC Dordrecht]].
Janga was born in the Netherlands to parents of [[Curaçaoans in the Netherlands|Curaçaoan descent]]. He was called up, and debuted for the [[Curaçao national football team]] in a 1-0 loss against [[Barbados national football team|Barbados]] in March 2016.<ref>http://www.fcdordrecht.nl/2016/03/24/internationals-fc-dordrecht-in-actie/</ref>
==Career== ===Club=== On 20 July 2018, Janga signed for [[FC Astana|Astana]].<ref name="Rangelo Janga">{{cite web |title=Форвард Рангело Янга подписал контракт с Астаной |url=http://fcastana.kz/rus/news/8158 |website=fcastana.kz |publisher=FC Astana |accessdate=23 July 2018 |language=Russian |date=20 July 2018}}</ref>
