{{Infobox football club | nickname = | ground = Complexo Ferroviário de Gondola, Gondola, [[Mozambique]] | capacity = | season = | fullname = Clube Desportivo Universidade Pedagógica de Manica | founded = | chairman = | manager = | league = Moçambola | position = | }}
'''Clube Desportivo Universidade Pedagógica de Manica''' is a [[Association football|football]] club based in Gondola (near [[Chimoio]]), [[Manica Province]], [[Mozambique]], which currently competes in the [[Moçambola]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[RSSSF]]|title=Mozambique 2018|author=José Batalha|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesm/moz2018.html|date=11 May 2018|accessdate=16 May 2018}}</ref> UP Manica was promoted after winning the 2017 Moçambola 2 (Center Zone) championship, and the club's first season in the top level of Mozambican football will begin in 2018.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[RSSSF]]|title=Mozambique 2017|author=José Batalha|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesm/moz2017.html|date=1 March 2018|accessdate=16 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Jornal Notícias|trans-title=Preparations for Moçambola 2018: UP Manica the first to open its "workshops"|title=PREPARAÇÃO DO MOÇAMBOLA-2018: UP Manica a primeira a abrir as “oficinas”|url=http://jornalnoticias.co.mz/index.php/desporto/desporto-nacional/73951-preparacao-do-mocambola-2018-up-manica-a-primeira-a-abrir-as-oficinas.html|language=Portuguese|date=3 December 2017|accessdate=16 May 2018}}</ref>
